trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle navigation events in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer metoden som håndterer navigasjon hendelser i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The WizardNavigationEventHandler class represents the method that handles the navigation events <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.FinishButtonClick>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.NextButtonClick>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.PreviousButtonClick>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.SideBarButtonClick> for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> control and for controls that inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> control (such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control).
trans-unit.target: Klassen WizardNavigationEventHandler representerer metoden som håndterer navigasjon hendelser <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.FinishButtonClick>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.NextButtonClick>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.PreviousButtonClick>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.SideBarButtonClick>for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>kontrollere og kontrollene som arve fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard>kontrollen (som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard>kontrollen).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.SideBarButtonClick> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.PreviousButtonClick> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.NextButtonClick> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Wizard.FinishButtonClick>

trans-unit.source: When you create a WizardNavigationEventHandler delegate, you identify the method that will handle the event.
trans-unit.target: Når du oppretter en WizardNavigationEventHandler representant, må du identifisere metoden som håndterer hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: To associate the event with your event handler, add an instance of the delegate to the event.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil knytte hendelsen til hendelsesbehandlingen, må du legge til en forekomst av representanten i hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The event handler is called whenever the event occurs, unless you remove the delegate.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsesbehandlingen kalles når det oppstår hendelsen, med mindre du fjerner representanten.

trans-unit.source: For more information about event-handler delegates, see [NIB: Events and Delegates](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d98fd58b-fa4f-4598-8378-addf4355a115).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hendelsesbehandlingen representanter [NIB: hendelser og representanter](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d98fd58b-fa4f-4598-8378-addf4355a115).
